Package: plotDK
Title: Plot summary statistics as choropleth maps of danish administrative areas
Description: This package provides a ggplot2 frontend to plot summary statistics on danish provinces,
    regions, municipalities, and zipcodes. The needed geoms of each of the four levels are 
    inherent in the package, thus making these types of plots easy for the user. This is essentialy 
    an updated port of the previously available 'mapDK' package by Sebastian Barfort.
Version: 0.1.0.9001
Author: Kristian Stendorff Nielsen
Maintainer: Kristian Stendorff Nielsen <kristiansn123@gmail.com>
